<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        *{
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .container{
            /* background-color: rgb(16, 16, 46); */
            display: grid;
            grid-auto-rows: max-content;

            grid-template-columns: 0.7fr 1.5fr repeat(2,1fr) 2fr;
            grid-template-rows:repeat(10,1fr);
            /* padding: 10px; */
            /* grid-auto-flow:column;
            column-gap: 15px; */
            
            /* background-image:url("backgroundImg.png"); */
            column-gap: 15px; 
            height: 100vh;
            background-image:  linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(107, 108, 117, 0.52), rgba(19, 50, 117, 0.73)),url('productbackg.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
        }
        .text-box{
            color:rgb(255, 255, 255);
            font-size: 7.8rem;
            font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
            grid-column: 2/4;
            grid-row:3/4;
            /* padding: 15px; */
        }

        .intro-video{    
            /* position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%); */
            width: auto;
            grid-column: 4/6;
            grid-row:3/6;
            padding-top: 15px;
            padding-right: 15px;
            /* object-fit: fill; */
        }
        .description-box{
            color:rgb(255, 250, 250);
            font-family :"GothamRegular",-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Verdana,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,"Helvetica Neue",sans-serif;
            grid-column: 2/3;
            grid-row: 5/8;
            
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            line-height: 30px;
        }
        .subtitle{
            color:rgb(255, 255, 255);
            font-family :"GothamRegular",-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Verdana,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Oxygen-Sans,Ubuntu,Cantarell,"Helvetica Neue",sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            line-height: 30px;
            grid-column: 2/3;
            grid-row: 4/5;
            align-self:baseline;
            padding-top: 25px;
            
        }
        
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-box">AYUCI</div>
        <div class="intro-video">
            <video autoplay loop playsinline muted >
                <source src="intovidayuci.mp4" type="video/mp4">
            </video>
        </div>
        <div class="subtitle">
            HealthCare Management System
        </div>
        <div class="description-box">
            Ayuci is a medical management app that streamlines healthcare operations and automates routine tasks. From booking patient appointments to managing doctor and employee lists, Ayuci ensures efficient handling of essential services.  Perfect for hospitals and clinics, Ayuci integrates IPD and OPD services to keep patient records up-to-date and enhance overall operational efficiency.
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>